masterRows.name: Picnic Blanket
masterRows.description: A great day for a picnic! Food, drinks, and fun for all Digimon. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Vending Machine
masterRows.description: An error makes this dispense drinks without inserting cash. <color=#e75600>Digimon sometimes visit this machine to quench their thirst.</color> (6x5)

masterRows.name: Warped Tower
masterRows.description: Could the eerily warped form of this metal tower be symbolic of something? Many Digimon seem to enjoy its aesthetic. (7x7)

masterRows.name: Pansies (Blue)
masterRows.description: Violaceae Viola. A flower known to come in a variety of colors. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Pansies (Violet)
masterRows.description: Violaceae Viola. A flower known to come in a variety of colors. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Pansies (Yellow)
masterRows.description: Violaceae Viola. A flower known to come in a variety of colors. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Portable Potty
masterRows.description: When you gotta go, you gotta go. <color=#e75600>Please be sure to wash your hands after you're finished.</color> (7x7)

masterRows.name: Tent
masterRows.description: None can resist the urge to crawl into a tent. <color=#e75600>Even Digimon will slide in for a short rest.</color> (7x7)

masterRows.name: Barrel
masterRows.description: A wooden vessel made for storage. Not intended for throwing or riding atop while it rolls. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Flowers
masterRows.description: These flowers have no name, but are often observed blooming in even the hardest soil. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Refrigerator
masterRows.description: <color=#e75600>Hungry Digimon come to scavenge snacks out of this,</color> but nobody knows what powers it or who refills its contents. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Planter
masterRows.description: A planter for flowers and other decorative plants. Have Digimon suddenly found pleasure in gardening? (5x5)

masterRows.name: Giant Mushroom
masterRows.description: A giant, mutated mushroom. Whether it's edible or not is unknown, but <color=#e75600>hungry Digimon have been seen taking bites out of it.</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Gears
masterRows.description: An installation designed to teach how gears work. The gears move under an unknown power source. The black gears are a little unnerving... (5x5)

masterRows.name: Performance Stage
masterRows.description: Shine on center stage. <color=#e75600>Any Digimon who stand on the stage put on a show, causing a crowd to gather.</color> (9x6)

masterRows.name: Fountain
masterRows.description: A simple fountain with a soothing spray. <color=#e75600>Digimon can play and refresh themselves by the waterside.</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Cradle
masterRows.description: A place for <color=#e75600>Fresh Digimon to take naps.</color> The sight of them sleeping brings comfort to all. <color=#e75600>Rookie Digimon can be found playing around in it.</color> (6x6)

masterRows.name: Tram Car
masterRows.description: A tram car that suddenly appeared in DigiTown. <color=#E75600>Curious Digimon will climb on board,</color> but it lacks a power source or rails allowing it to move. Somewhat nostalgic. (9x6)

masterRows.name: Campfire
masterRows.description: <color=#E75600>Sitting quietly by the fire can put your mind at ease.</color> A nice, warm meal cooked over fire wouldn't hurt, either. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Butterfly
masterRows.description: A fickle and whimsical digital butterfly found in the Digital World. Alluring to those who see it, but <color=#e75600>disappears when approached</color>. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Watermelon
masterRows.description: Juicy and refreshing, watermelons are perfect snacks for the summer! Still, Digimon have just as much fun <color=#E75600>smashing them to pieces as they do eating them</color>. (6x5)

masterRows.name: Tilted Traffic Signs
masterRows.description: Traffic signs from the real world that phased into DigiTown. Their chaotic arrangement will lead you nowhere. (7x7)

masterRows.name: Punching Machine
masterRows.description: It may look nice and cheerful, but it's a rather aggressive facility.<color=#E75600>The Digimon inside are doing their best, but those who lack training sometimes find it's more than they can handle...</color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: Tombstone
masterRows.description: A place where someone's soul is laid to rest. A <color=#E75600>certain Digimon</color> is said to live within, a rumor that <color=#E75600>several eyewitnesses</color> have attested to. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Jack-o'-Lantern
masterRows.description: A pumpkin decoration for Halloween. <color=#E75600>Digimon will gather around it</color> in high spirits. (5x5)

masterRows.name: Jumbo Jack-o'-Lantern
masterRows.description: A pumpkin decoration for Halloween. All the candy makes for a jovial Halloween mood. <color=#E75600>But then, from inside the lantern...!</color> Talk about "Trick or Treat"! (6x5)

masterRows.name: Withered Tree & Candlesticks
masterRows.description: This eerie dead tree is home to spiderwebs, soaring bats and creepy candles, adding a splash of horror to your DigiTown. (5x6)

masterRows.name: Phone Booth
masterRows.description: This telephone is a rare sight in the real world. <color=#e75600>Digimon can get startled by the sudden ringing of a phone.</color> Who could be calling? (5x5)

masterRows.name: Christmas Tree
masterRows.description: Your run-of-the-mill Christmas tree. <color=#E75600>Digimon gather around, waiting with glee for the festivities to begin.</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Thanksgiving Garden Party
masterRows.description: <color=#E75600>Your Digimon will have a blast, surrounded by these delicacies</color> made specially for the Thanksgiving Garden Party. (6x5)

masterRows.name: Great Chestnut Tree
masterRows.description: A tree filled with sizeable chestnuts, perfect to satisfy one's autumn appetite. <color=#E75600>But if you get too greedy...</color> (5x6)

masterRows.name: Pansies (Red)
masterRows.description: Violaceae Viola. A flower known to come in a variety of colors. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Dinosaur Sculpture
masterRows.description: A dinosaur sculpture found in a certain park. <color=#E75600>Digimon can be found chatting and playing games inside.</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Illuminated Tree
masterRows.description: A glittering and stylish Christmas Tree. <color=#E75600>A place of healing for Digimon who are drawn to the beautiful lights.</color> (6x6)

masterRows.name: Santa's Sleigh
masterRows.description: A personal sleigh that Santa Claus uses to fly high in the sky. Will the Digimon get Christmas presents? (5x6)

masterRows.name: 亥年の門松
masterRows.description: 新年になると現れるかわいい門松。お正月の晴れやかな雰囲気がデジタウンを包み込む。あけましておめでとうございます。(6x6)

masterRows.name: Festive Rice Cake
masterRows.description: A rice cake grilled beside the Festive Rice Cake. <color=#E75600>Digimon can eat the fluffy grilled delicacy or sit atop the Festive Rice Cake! There are plenty of ways for your Digimon to enjoy this item.</color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: Winter Puddle
masterRows.description: A puddle that has frozen due to the coldness of winter. <color=#E75600>You'll probably get an urge to walk on it, but be plenty careful if you do...!</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Snowman
masterRows.description: A simple snowman. It's simple appearance <color=#e75600>is what sparks a Digimon's appetite for creativity</color>. (6x6)

masterRows.name: Snow-covered Tree
masterRows.description: A tree covered in tons of snow. <color=#e75600>Digimon will get excited about this, but watch out for falling snow!</color> Best to be safe and not stand under it... (5x6)

masterRows.name: Igloo
masterRows.description: A mysterious igloo that fits Digimon of any size. Surprisingly, the inside is warm <color=#E75600>and is a place of relaxation for Digimon.</color>. (6x6)

masterRows.name: 節分の枡
masterRows.description: 豆が山盛りに入った節分の枡。<color=#E75600>大量の豆に埋もれてみたい衝動を抑えきれなかったデジモン</color>がいるらしい。(6x6)

masterRows.name: Punching Ball
masterRows.description: A training installation used for practicing punches. <color=#e75600>Some Digimon just like to play with its bouncy nature.</color> (5x5)

masterRows.name: Giant Chocolate Bar
masterRows.description:
A Giant Chocolate Bar is now available to help
set the Valentine's Day mood in your DigiTown.
<color=#E75600>You may even witness some unexpected
heart-pounding moments...!</color> (5x6)

masterRows.name: Retro Computer
masterRows.description: A computer from the distant past. Though this one is still pretty bulky, some were said to have filled up the entire gym.<color=#e75600> Most Digimon will give it a whirl but won't be able to make much sense of it. A tech-savvy Digimon might find a use for it however. </color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: Cherry Blossoms
masterRows.description: Cherry Blossoms in full bloom. Looking at cherry blossoms can stir feelings within even the most stoic of people, but nothing's quite as heartwarming as watching <color=#E75600>Digimon frolic together</color>. (6x6)

masterRows.name: Traffic Cone
masterRows.description: These are used to sort and regulate traffic in the real world, but aren't very effective for corralling Digimon. Looks pretty beat up. (5x5)

masterRows.name: レトロなテレビ
masterRows.description: ひと昔前のテレビ。様々な人に情報を伝えていたが世代交代の荒波にもまれ、今はその役目を終えている……？<color=#e75600>デジモンが近くにいるとひょっこりと何か映ることがあるかもしれない。</color>(5x6)

masterRows.name: 1周年記念のデジタルサイネージ
masterRows.description: 1周年を記念して作られたデジタルな看板。(5x5)

masterRows.name: 1周年記念のお祝いケーキ
masterRows.description: 1周年を記念した特注のケーキ。<color=#E75600>なかよく分け合ってデジモン達は大満足。</color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: 1周年記念のお祝い花火
masterRows.description: 1周年を記念したド派手な花火。<color=#E75600>花火の迫力にデジモンたちも大興奮。</color>(5x7)

masterRows.name: 1周年記念のお祝い看板
masterRows.description: 1周年を記念したスペシャルな立て看板。<color=#E75600>デジモン達も看板の前に集まって1周年をお祝い。</color>(5x7)

masterRows.name: Poop
masterRows.description: An ornament of...Sukamon's handmade poop. Fear not, this is only a replica! Comes odor-free so you won't get sick from it. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Golden Poop
masterRows.description: An ornament of...Sukamon's handmade golden poop. The glossy finish really shows off the artisan's passion. (1x1) <color=#e75600>Passable</color>

masterRows.name: Bonfire
masterRows.description: Digimon too, enjoy a good fire. <color=#e75600>Up to four Digimon will dance cheerfully around the fire.</color> (7x7)

masterRows.name: クリスマスツリー(2019)
masterRows.description: エリスモンの姿を象ったクリスマスツリー。<color=#E75600>集まったデジモンたちが輪になって楽しそうな姿を見せる。</color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: 聖夜のパーティセット
masterRows.description: 2019年のクリスマスのために用意された<color=#E75600>ごちそうを囲んでデジモンたちがワイワイと楽しい時間を過ごす。</color>(5x7)

masterRows.name: プレゼントの山
masterRows.description: 見るだけで心がワクワクするプレゼントの山。<color=#E75600>その中にカタカタと動く怪しい箱。その正体を見たデジモンは思わずビックリ。</color>(6x6)

masterRows.name: 新年の銅像(2020)
masterRows.description: 新年を記念して造られた銅像。デジタウンの新しいランドマークになるかもしれない…！？(5x5)

masterRows.name: Moai Statue
masterRows.description: Stone statues found on a certain island in the real world. Where did they come from? And how did they end up in your DigiTown? (6x5)
